// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0162 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: dda1a314-c83b-5f4d-9b57-720b915ed687

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*wolfi:*")
